---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Terms — appelsin" locale="en">
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12">
		<a href="/en" class="mb-8 inline-block text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200">← Home</a>
		<h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Terms</h1>
		<div class="space-y-5 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300">
			<p>
				appelsin.io is used for live photo sharing at events. By creating or using an event, you agree to use the service responsibly and only upload content you have the right to share.
			</p>
			<p>
				The event host is responsible for telling guests how photos are used at the event. Photos may be shown live on the event screen and are kept for the retention window that applies to the chosen plan.
			</p>
			<p>
				We may remove content or block access if the service is misused, or if illegal, infringing, or harmful content is uploaded.
			</p>
			<p>
				Paid event passes and subscriptions are processed via Stripe. Event passes apply to a single event; subscriptions follow the terms shown at purchase.
			</p>
			<p>
				Contact us at <a class="underline hover:text-white" href="mailto:hello@appelsin.io">hello@appelsin.io</a> if you have questions about the terms.
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
